TY  - JOUR
TI  - Finite Sample Distributions Associated with Stochastic Difference Equations--Some Experimental Evidence
AU  - Basmann, R. L.
AU  - Richardson, D. H.
AU  - Rohr, R. J.
AB  - [The empirical distribution functions of the least squares estimators and test statistics in a system of stochastic difference equation are studied. The general conclusion is that the empirical distributions cannot be closely approximated using the normal distribution theory.]
