TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Nontransitive Consumer
AU  - Shafer, Wayne J.
AB  - [A consistent theory of demand is possible without the transitivity axiom. Here it is shown that a class of nontransitive orderings can be represented by a continuous numerical function, in such a way that an individual's demand function may be found by solving a constrained maximum problem.]
